Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:30.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}世界仰望天际时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}牠们仍俯视看着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:38.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}在环抱擦伤的双膝的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:43.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}一直在等待有人能够到来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:51.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}理所当然的事物 并非理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:56.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}正是因为失去了才懂得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:21:59.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}冻结的笑容伤害了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:02.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}即使如此 笑容仍治愈了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:04.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}你所凝望的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}突然消失无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:09.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}扑空的手就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:14.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}那紧握的未来正是你啊
