Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:24.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}太陽が西を歌い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:26.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}星が東を指すとき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:28.37,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}窓辺に止まる鳥は飛び立った
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:30.56,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}世界が空を見上げても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}下を向いていた
